Package: pkgfilecache
Type: Package
Title: Allow Users of Your Package to Download and Manage Optional Package Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tim Schäfer
Maintainer: Tim Schäfer <ts+code@rcmd.org>
Description: Allows users to download and manage optional data for your package. The data can be hosted anywhere, and you have to give a Uniform Resource Locator (URL) for each file. File integrity checks are supported. This is useful for package authors who need to ship more than the 5 Megabyte of data currently allowed by the the Comprehensive R Archive Network (CRAN).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/dfsp-spirit/pkgfilecache
BugReports: https://github.com/dfsp-spirit/pkgfilecache/issues
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
Imports:
